{"tid":353282,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"喇叭大神入黎幫幫手","createTime":"2017-08-09T12:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T11:24:32.000Z","uid":80720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f4da56f711ff0c24992e92c23f96443f8e1d627c","tid":353282,"uid":80720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T12:48:11.000Z","msg":"小弟近排將係廳既電腦搬返入房<br />\n裝返好哂d野 發現喇叭得返右邊有聲<br />\n<br />\n試過用手機插播歌冇問題<br />\n左右都有聲 (USB插口）<br />\n<br />\n排除咗喇叭壞呢個原因<br />\n<br />\n連返去電腦/ps4 <br />\n得返右邊有邊（3.5mm插口）<br />\n<br />\n電腦同PS4左右聲道確保正常<br />\n<br />\n我想問下係咪個喇叭既乸3.5mm出左問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇咩方法解決？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：換哂所有線 差個喇叭內置3.5mm未換（唔識換）<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以教下小弟"},{"pid":"ce22d42f524e58d098596543d2ee73a45eb62d18","tid":353282,"uid":80720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T12:49:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510d772390306b84881c3d63c05e29cfcba51a08","tid":353282,"uid":80720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:07:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/210659_3899c2b20b216beffdc2cbbdd5c0c01a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F210659_3899c2b20b216beffdc2cbbdd5c0c01a.jpg&h=222dcafa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/210701_4ca0830d569903789600b0b6218adbe3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F210701_4ca0830d569903789600b0b6218adbe3.jpg&h=fb6246c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋呢隻款係咪拆唔到黎睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b770a35d5